WHEREAS, the Individual is or will be employed by or engaged with the Company in the capacity of {{job_title}};

WHEREAS, the Individual will have access to the Company's confidential information, trade secrets, customer relationships, and proprietary business methods;

WHEREAS, the Company has a legitimate business interest in protecting its confidential information, customer relationships, and competitive position;

NOW, THEREFORE, in consideration of the mutual promises and covenants contained herein, and for other good and valuable consideration, the Parties agree as follows.

In exchange for the Individual's agreement to the restrictions contained in this Agreement, the Company shall provide the following consideration:

{{consideration_description}}

The Individual acknowledges that the consideration provided is adequate and sufficient.

During the Restricted Period, the Individual shall not, directly or indirectly:

(a) Solicit, contact, or attempt to solicit any customer, client, or account of the Company for the purpose of providing competing products or services;
(b) Solicit, recruit, or attempt to recruit any employee, contractor, or consultant of the Company;
(c) Encourage or induce any customer, supplier, or business partner to terminate or reduce their relationship with the Company.
